  branch's inherited suitable-weak / Leray-Hopf plus LEI architecture.

So the obstruction is not "no compactness rhetoric." It is that the compactness
language never becomes one architecture-compatible extraction package.

The correct Step-1 label is therefore:
`not viable because extraction package is diffuse`.

